# Environment variables for mujoco-browser.
#
# This project is designed to run fully offline in the browser — there are no
# LLM API keys, no backend services, and no external fetches at runtime. The
# few build-time overrides below are optional.

# Vite base path for production build (used when deploying to GitHub Pages
# under a subpath, e.g. "/mujoco-browser/"). Leave unset for root deploys.
# VITE_BASE=/mujoco-browser/
